g.text: THE HARDWARE TAX: MICROSCOPIC EXECUTION VIEW

g.title: ### The Ideal Path Data sits in the L1 Cache (SRAM). The CPU execution unit retrieves it in **~1ns**. The instruction pipeline remains full.
### The Taxed Path Data is missing from all caches (L1, L2, L3). The **Pager** must request a page from DRAM. The CPU stalls for **~100ns (400 cycles)**.
